Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.35,0:01:37.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從谷川岳BASE PLAZA這個地方搭乘纜車去天神平
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.65,0:01:41.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從那裏坐登山電梯登上天神卡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.07,0:01:44.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,纜車和登山電梯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.57,0:01:48.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了登上回憶的大山 逃避可是過不去的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.62,0:01:50.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.33,0:01:54.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心情還是很沉重啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.96,0:01:57.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葵恐高呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.34,0:02:03.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說葵 我有個地方想去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.92,0:02:05.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想去的地方？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.80,0:02:08.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,偶爾也去大山以外的地方玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.72,0:02:15.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為日向的提案 大家一起出門了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.24,0:02:19.36,title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(572,426)}高處沒關係嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.02,0:02:24.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歡迎來到武藏丘陵森林公園
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.40,0:02:28.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看起來很大呀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.82,0:02:31.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽說有65個東京巨蛋那麼大
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.08,0:02:36.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,公園裏還有巴士呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.04,0:02:38.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有很多可以玩的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.33,0:02:41.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一天可玩不過來哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.55,0:02:46.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琦玉海盜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.01,0:02:49.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在幹什麼呀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.43,0:02:53.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海盜啦海盜 小的們 起錨啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.31,0:02:59.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,滑梯從小學起就沒玩過了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.90,0:03:01.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.07,0:03:07.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好高呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.36,0:03:08.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,景色真不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.16,0:03:10.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們倆真厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.16,0:03:12.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很有趣的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.91,0:03:14.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葵也來試試啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.16,0:03:18.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這種高度沒問題的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.79,0:03:19.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.42,0:03:23.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼樣 沒什麼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.71,0:03:26.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 這種高度的話沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.38,0:03:32.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心夏好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.43,0:03:37.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鞦韆大概從小學起也沒玩過了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.27,0:03:40.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,楓 來玩飛鞋吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.23,0:03:46.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做好覺悟了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.65,0:03:47.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你才是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.99,0:03:50.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看誰重 一二
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.53,0:03:55.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日向更重
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.58,0:03:59.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我長得更高 當然會重
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.75,0:04:02.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才高3cm而已 沒什麼區別吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.67,0:04:05.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算3cm 也是我贏了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.13,0:04:07.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在說的是體重吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.46,0:04:09.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心夏 準備好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.05,0:04:10.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.05,0:04:11.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.89,0:04:17.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葵
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.97,0:04:19.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葵也去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.93,0:04:21.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼呀 真囉嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.23,0:04:28.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,風吹著好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.95,0:04:33.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼樣 葵
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.49,0:04:36.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 完全沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.12,0:04:40.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對吧 嗯嗯 沒事 沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.08,0:04:45.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,屁股好熱呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.96,0:04:47.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 葵
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.54,0:04:49.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像很開心呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.72,0:04:55.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐你不滑嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.14,0:04:57.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你先請 你先請
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.43,0:05:04.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自行車看起來也很舒服呀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.48,0:05:06.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巴士來了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.45,0:05:15.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古鐮倉街道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.61,0:05:17.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有歷史呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.37,0:05:20.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這條路通到鐮倉和小田原呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.16,0:05:23.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以前的人真厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.87,0:05:27.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我登個富士山都精疲力盡了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.29,0:05:32.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鳥巢 有沒有鼯鼠或者飛鼠呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.72,0:05:34.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,松鼠倒是有哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.14,0:05:38.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.06,0:05:46.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好涼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.40,0:05:47.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真舒服呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.44,0:05:52.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心夏 那個你打算怎麼弄呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.90,0:05:56.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竹葉呢 像這樣 這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.99,0:05:58.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是竹葉船呀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.37,0:05:58.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.87,0:06:06.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有這種用法哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.67,0:06:15.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 我想該吃午飯了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.30,0:06:16.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肚子都餓死了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.09,0:06:20.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都帶自己親手做的便當了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.60,0:06:21.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當然了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.89,0:06:25.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為約好了大家一起帶便當過來呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.43,0:06:28.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不准帶凍結乾燥食品 我可費了好大勁呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.98,0:06:31.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就先從葵的便當開始
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.69,0:06:33.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.90,0:06:34.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.99,0:06:37.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下了一番功夫呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.70,0:06:39.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上五點起來做的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.91,0:06:41.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,挺能幹的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.37,0:06:43.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼一副高高在上的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.08,0:06:45.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下一個是心夏
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.62,0:06:47.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的 我的是這個
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.33,0:06:50.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.04,0:06:53.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,主題是妖精的點心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.67,0:06:58.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我覺得有點甜食也不錯 早上六點起來做了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.30,0:07:01.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯嗯 花樣豐富不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.89,0:07:04.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以說為什麼一副高高在上的樣子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.85,0:07:06.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下一個是楓
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.56,0:07:09.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 不要笑我哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.73,0:07:17.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個是梅子的 這個是柴魚乾的 還有金槍魚和昆布
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.49,0:07:18.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看起來很好吃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.90,0:07:21.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的食慾都被刺激出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.20,0:07:23.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這種豪放感很不錯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.28,0:07:25.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以說為什麼一副高高在上的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.54,0:07:28.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話說 日向把你的便當給我們看看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.75,0:07:34.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想看？想看？真拿你們沒辦法 都這麼說了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.92,0:07:37.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我非常想看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.59,0:07:38.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是這個哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.81,0:07:48.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個絕對不是日向做的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.31,0:07:49.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,露餡了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.60,0:07:52.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是爸爸早上三點鐘起來做的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.81,0:07:54.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幹勁十足呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.90,0:07:56.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還說什麼幹勁十足呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.57,0:07:58.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上三點還是夜裏吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.07,0:07:59.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,開吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.28,0:08:02.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.32,0:08:06.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 好吃 楓 柴魚幹好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.62,0:08:07.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.74,0:08:09.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葵 我可以吃干炸嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.58,0:08:10.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請用 請用
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.21,0:08:14.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個水果西紅柿 又甜又好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.08,0:08:15.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.59,0:08:19.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在大自然中和大家一起吃飯 真不錯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.42,0:08:20.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.30,0:08:24.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了 吃完飯我有個想去的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.14,0:08:26.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想去的地方？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.22,0:08:31.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想…想去的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.90,0:08:34.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吊橋？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.77,0:08:37.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葵 沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.69,0:08:39.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒那麼高啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.49,0:08:41.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不怎麼晃的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.16,0:08:45.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.49,0:08:47.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我還是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.91,0:08:48.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,害怕…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.87,0:08:49.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葵
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.21,0:08:56.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葵
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.92,0:08:58.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.72,0:09:02.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.47,0:09:04.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日向
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.93,0:09:09.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看前面 不要急 慢慢走
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.68,0:09:12.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要看下面
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.06,0:09:14.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.94,0:09:15.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日向
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.73,0:09:22.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道是因為我害怕登山電梯和纜車
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.49,0:09:25.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想讓我習慣高處嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.74,0:09:27.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才到這個公園裏來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.66,0:09:32.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的吧 她就是有這樣的地方呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.54,0:09:36.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看 沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.58,0:09:38.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做到了呢 葵
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.88,0:09:39.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.55,0:09:44.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 日向 謝謝…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.05,0:09:47.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後那個是空氣蹦床
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.39,0:09:50.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蹦床？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.11,0:10:00.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐真厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.15,0:10:02.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們是小孩子麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.49,0:10:06.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 葵
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.45,0:10:07.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到這來呀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.16,0:10:10.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常好玩哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.74,0:10:12.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在這裏就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.12,0:10:14.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那邊很高呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.37,0:10:16.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.63,0:10:22.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去一下看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.85,0:10:35.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再往上走走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.73,0:10:41.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比小的更有彈性
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.23,0:10:42.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個說不定很有趣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.63,0:11:03.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葵 日向
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.46,0:11:04.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.59,0:11:08.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玩過火了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.34,0:11:09.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起 日向
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.05,0:11:11.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比起那個 葵
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.85,0:11:13.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在高處完全沒事嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.27,0:11:19.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是真的 一點都沒害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.35,0:11:23.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為很開心？因為非常專注？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.23,0:11:27.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日向 謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.74,0:11:29.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.70,0:11:33.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.16,0:11:35.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過 謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.41,0:11:43.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然我還是害怕高處 但是只要和日向和大家在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.50,0:11:47.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,纜車什麼的 登山電梯什麼的 感覺都可以超越
